title: Avoid L2 Computer unless you want junk: 820-2914 216-0810005
message: Even fixing the DEVID of the 3000 chip which will get boot screen it will not solve the sensor errors that the SMC will produce because it will not read any sensors related to GPU because of an unsupported DEVID. Without being able to fix the SMC firmware there is no way to get a 3000 chip to work at a hardware level. Then there is no software support for this DEVID, so this project is DOA.

title: Avoid L2 Computer unless you want junk: 820-2914 216-0810005
message: It's the SMC that's fucked it. Hacking the OS to run this chip is easy.... SMC thermal sensors permanently curtails the 3000 chip from ever being used.
